# Styling (Essential)

- Use styled-components only.
- Always read tokens from theme (colors, spacing, typography, radius, shadows).
- Reuse [src/styles/section.ts](mdc:src/styles/section.ts) for section layout/title.
- Extract section-local styles into `*.styles.ts`.
- Links: subtle underline; hover color = theme.colors.primary.
- Global resets via `GlobalStyle`.
